short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: 180 flip Hacker News, so Australians can read it.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Australians have their work cut out for them, viewing everything on the internet upside down. “Hacker Kangaroos” adjusts Hacker News to be easily viewed in the proper orientation a full 180-degree flip. Good luck mate.

Also works well in any country in the southern hemisphere.

Made with <3 by Agency Enterprise as part of Same Day Skunkworks.
